@rtheys I think i saw this few issues few days back.

You need to update `/usr/share/containers/seccomp.json` on your host. You could pull latest https://github.com/containers/common and do `make seccomp.json` and move file to seccomp to right location or just simply update `containers-common` pkg for centos.

Edit: I think image needs to be updated. What happens with `:latest` tag ?
